<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Wonder Tales - Project Detail</title>

    <!-- Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Chakra+Petch:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Fira+Code:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- Tailwind CSS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        navy: '#0a0505', /* Very dark red/black */
                        red: {
                            500: '#ef4444',
                            600: '#dc2626',
                            800: '#991b1b',
                            900: '#7f1d1d',
                        },
                        'cinnabar': '#e53e3e',
                        white: '#fff1f2',
                        'deep-blue': '#00008B',
                        'neon-green': '#39ff14',
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Inter', 'system-ui', 'sans-serif'],
                        serif: ['Noto Serif SC', 'serif'],
                        mono: ['Fira Code', 'monospace'],
                        display: ['Chakra Petch', 'sans-serif'],
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>

    <!-- Icons -->
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>

    <style>
        /* Global Overrides */
        :root {
            --navy: #0a0505;
            --cinnabar: #e53e3e;
            --dark-red: #7f1d1d;
            --neon-green: #39ff14;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--navy);
            color: #fca5a5;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Scrollbar */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 8px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: #0a0505;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background-color: #7f1d1d;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background-color: var(--cinnabar);
        }

        ::selection {
            background-color: #7f1d1d;
            color: white;
        }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .animate-fade-in {
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
            opacity: 0;
        }
        
        .delay-100 { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .delay-200 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .delay-300 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }

        .lang-zh { display: none; }
        body.zh-mode .lang-en { display: none; }
        body.zh-mode .lang-zh { display: block; }
        body.zh-mode span.lang-zh { display: inline; }
        body.zh-mode span.lang-en { display: none; }

        /* Edgy Design */
        .clip-sharp {
            clip-path: polygon(
                0 0,
                100% 0,
                100% calc(100% - 20px),
                calc(100% - 20px) 100%,
                0 100%
            );
        }
        
        /* Red Panel Style */
        .red-glass-panel {
            background: rgba(127, 29, 29, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: relative;
        }

        .red-border-frame {
            border: 2px solid var(--cinnabar);
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(229, 62, 62, 0.3);
            position: relative;
        }

        .red-border-frame::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            right: -5px;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--cinnabar);
            border-right: 2px solid var(--cinnabar);
        }

        /* Chinese Pattern Overlay */
        .chinese-pattern {
            background-image: radial-gradient(var(--dark-red) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body class="antialiased font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col">

    <!-- Navbar (Red Theme) -->
    <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 bg-navy/90 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-lg border-b border-red-900/50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between h-20">
                <!-- Back to Projects -->
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 relative group cursor-pointer animate-fade-in">
                    <a href="projects.html" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-red-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        <span class="font-display font-bold">BACK</span>
                    </a>
                </div>

                <!-- Project Menu -->
                <div class="hidden md:block">
                    <div class="ml-10 flex items-center space-x-8">
                        <a href="#summary" class="text-white hover:text-red-500 font-display px-2 py-1 transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">
                            <span class="lang-en">Summary</span><span class="lang-zh">概览</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#pillars" class="text-white hover:text-red-500 font-display px-2 py-1 transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">
                            <span class="lang-en">Pillars</span><span class="lang-zh">核心支柱</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#characters" class="text-white hover:text-red-500 font-display px-2 py-1 transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">
                            <span class="lang-en">Characters</span><span class="lang-zh">角色</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#setting" class="text-white hover:text-red-500 font-display px-2 py-1 transition-colors uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">
                            <span class="lang-en">Setting</span><span class="lang-zh">背景设定</span>
                        </a>

                        <!-- Lang Toggle -->
                        <button onclick="toggleLang()" class="text-red-500 hover:bg-red-500 hover:text-white p-2 transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-2 border border-red-500 font-mono text-xs ml-4">
                            <i data-lucide="globe" class="w-4 h-4"></i>
                            <span class="lang-en">CN</span><span class="lang-zh">EN</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Mobile Menu Button -->
                <div class="md:hidden">
                    <button onclick="toggleMobileMenu()" class="text-red-500 hover:text-white p-2 border border-red-500">
                        <i data-lucide="menu" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mobile Menu -->
        <div id="mobile-menu" class="hidden md:hidden bg-navy px-2 pt-2 pb-3 space-y-1 sm:px-3 border-b border-red-900">
            <a href="#summary" class="text-white hover:text-red-500 block px-3 py-4 text-base font-medium font-display border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-red-500 transition-all">Summary</a>
            <a href="#pillars" class="text-white hover:text-red-500 block px-3 py-4 text-base font-medium font-display border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-red-500 transition-all">Pillars</a>
            <a href="#characters" class="text-white hover:text-red-500 block px-3 py-4 text-base font-medium font-display border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-red-500 transition-all">Characters</a>
            <a href="#setting" class="text-white hover:text-red-500 block px-3 py-4 text-base font-medium font-display border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-red-500 transition-all">Setting</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="pt-20">
        
        <!-- Banner / Hero -->
        <section id="summary" class="relative min-h-[85vh] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-navy">
            <!-- Background Image -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
                <img src="images/wonder-tales-cover.jpg" alt="Cover" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 mix-blend-luminosity">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-navy via-navy/80 to-transparent"></div>
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-navy via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 w-full grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                
                <!-- Text Content -->
                <div class="space-y-8 animate-fade-in delay-100">
                    <div class="inline-block border-2 border-red-500 px-4 py-1 text-red-500 font-mono text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">
                        Project Detail
                    </div>
                    
                    <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-display font-bold text-white tracking-tighter leading-none" style="text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #7f1d1d;">
                        WONDER<br>TALES
                    </h1>
                    
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-red-500 pl-6 py-4 bg-red-900/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
                        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white font-serif italic leading-relaxed opacity-90">
                            <span class="lang-en">"A haunting journey through ancient China, blending fear, the supernatural, and deep stories about love, betrayal, and friendship."</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">“一段穿越古代中国的诡秘旅程，融合了恐惧、超自然力量，以及关于爱、背叛与友谊的深沉故事。”</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-red-200 text-lg font-light leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
                        <span class="lang-en">Wonder Tales is a narrative-driven RPG that mixes ancient Chinese folklore with Western-style supernatural horror (Cthulhu Mythos). Players take on the role of a Western protagonist exploring a mystical version of ancient China.</span>
                        <span class="lang-zh">Wonder Tales 是一款叙事驱动的 RPG，将中国古代民间传说与西式超自然恐怖（克苏鲁神话）相结合。玩家将扮演一名西方主角，探索一个神秘的古代中国。</span>
                    </p>
                    
                    <div class="flex gap-4 pt-4">
                         <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-red-900/30 border border-red-500/50 text-red-300 text-xs font-mono uppercase">RPG / Visual Novel</div>
                         <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-red-900/30 border border-red-500/50 text-red-300 text-xs font-mono uppercase">Horror</div>
                         <div class="px-4 py-2 bg-red-900/30 border border-red-500/50 text-red-300 text-xs font-mono uppercase">Narrative</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right Side Visual Element -->
                <div class="hidden lg:block relative h-full min-h-[500px] border-2 border-red-900/30 bg-red-900/5 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 flex items-center justify-center">
                    <div class="text-center space-y-6">
                        <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto border border-red-500 rotate-45 flex items-center justify-center">
                            <div class="w-24 h-24 border border-red-500 rotate-90"></div>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif text-white uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">1797</h3>
                        <p class="text-red-400 font-mono text-sm">QING DYNASTY x MISKATONIC UNIV.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Game Pillars Section -->
        <section id="pillars" class="py-24 bg-[#0f0505] relative border-t border-red-900/30">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-16 text-center uppercase tracking-widest">
                    <span class="lang-en">Game Pillars</span>
                    <span class="lang-zh">核心支柱</span>
                </h2>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                    <!-- Pillar 1 -->
                    <div class="red-glass-panel p-6 hover:bg-red-900/20 transition-colors group">
                        <div class="text-red-500 mb-4 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">01</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display uppercase">
                            <span class="lang-en">Replayability</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">多周目体验</span>
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-sm text-red-200/70 leading-relaxed">
                            <span class="lang-en">Meet different NPCs, unlock multiple endings, and experience storylines shaped by your choices.</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">邂逅不同的NPC，解锁多种结局，体验由你的选择塑造的独特故事线。</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Pillar 2 -->
                    <div class="red-glass-panel p-6 hover:bg-red-900/20 transition-colors group">
                         <div class="text-red-500 mb-4 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">02</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display uppercase">
                            <span class="lang-en">Cards</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">卡牌系统</span>
                        </h3>
                         <p class="text-sm text-red-200/70 leading-relaxed">
                            <span class="lang-en">Collect character cards, unlock special plots, and upgrade them to reveal personal stories.</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">收集角色卡牌，解锁特殊剧情，升级卡牌以揭示深层个人故事。</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Pillar 3 -->
                    <div class="red-glass-panel p-6 hover:bg-red-900/20 transition-colors group">
                         <div class="text-red-500 mb-4 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">03</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display uppercase">
                            <span class="lang-en">Relationships</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">人际关系</span>
                        </h3>
                         <p class="text-sm text-red-200/70 leading-relaxed">
                            <span class="lang-en">Build connections with NPCs. Choose from 4 playable characters, each with unique backgrounds.</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">与NPC建立联系。从4名背景各异的可玩角色中选择，体验不同的人际羁绊。</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Pillar 4 -->
                    <div class="red-glass-panel p-6 hover:bg-red-900/20 transition-colors group">
                         <div class="text-red-500 mb-4 opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">04</div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3 font-display uppercase">
                            <span class="lang-en">Collections</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">收集要素</span>
                        </h3>
                         <p class="text-sm text-red-200/70 leading-relaxed">
                            <span class="lang-en">Collect items, weapons, and cards. Unlock new endings through meaningful exploration.</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">收集物品、武器与卡牌。通过有意义的探索解锁全新结局。</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Characters Section -->
        <section id="characters" class="py-24 bg-navy relative overflow-hidden">
             <!-- Chinese Pattern Background -->
            <div class="absolute inset-0 chinese-pattern pointer-events-none"></div>

            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-12 text-center uppercase tracking-widest">
                    <span class="lang-en">Investigators</span>
                    <span class="lang-zh">调查员</span>
                </h2>
                
                <p class="text-center text-red-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 font-light text-lg">
                    <span class="lang-en">Four recent graduates of Miskatonic University. They share similar traits but exist in parallel worlds—choosing a character determines which storyline you follow.</span>
                    <span class="lang-zh">四位密斯卡塔尼克大学的应届毕业生。他们虽有相似之处，却身处平行世界——选择一名角色，即选择了你将经历的独特故事线。</span>
                </p>

                <!-- Character Grid -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 md:gap-8">
                    <!-- Char 1 -->
                    <div class="group relative aspect-[3/5] overflow-hidden border border-red-900/50 bg-black/50 hover:border-red-500 transition-colors">
                        <img src="images/wonder-tales-char1.png" alt="Character 1" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100">
                        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent p-4 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300">
                            <p class="text-white font-display text-sm">INVESTIGATOR 01</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Char 2 -->
                    <div class="group relative aspect-[3/5] overflow-hidden border border-red-900/50 bg-black/50 hover:border-red-500 transition-colors">
                        <img src="images/wonder-tales-char2.png" alt="Character 2" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100">
                         <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent p-4 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300">
                            <p class="text-white font-display text-sm">INVESTIGATOR 02</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Char 3 -->
                    <div class="group relative aspect-[3/5] overflow-hidden border border-red-900/50 bg-black/50 hover:border-red-500 transition-colors">
                        <img src="images/wonder-tales-char3.png" alt="Character 3" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100">
                         <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent p-4 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300">
                            <p class="text-white font-display text-sm">INVESTIGATOR 03</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Char 4 -->
                    <div class="group relative aspect-[3/5] overflow-hidden border border-red-900/50 bg-black/50 hover:border-red-500 transition-colors">
                        <img src="images/wonder-tales-char4.png" alt="Character 4" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100">
                         <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-full bg-gradient-to-t from-black to-transparent p-4 translate-y-full group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-transform duration-300">
                            <p class="text-white font-display text-sm">INVESTIGATOR 04</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Setting Section -->
        <section id="setting" class="py-24 bg-[#1a0505] relative border-t border-red-900/30">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
                <div class="red-border-frame p-8 md:p-12 bg-navy/80 relative">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-8 border-b border-red-900 pb-4">
                        <span class="lang-en">The Setting: 1797 China</span>
                        <span class="lang-zh">背景设定：1797年 中国</span>
                    </h2>
                    
                    <div class="space-y-6 text-red-100/80 leading-relaxed font-light">
                        <p>
                            <span class="lang-en">The game is set in 1797 (Qing Dynasty), when China was mostly closed to the outside world. This setting mixes historical fact with fictional mysticism, creating a rich backdrop for exploration.</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">游戏设定在1797年（清朝），当时中国对外界基本封闭。这一设定将历史事实与虚构的神秘主义相结合，为探索创造了丰富的背景。</span>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <span class="lang-en">In 1798, each protagonist enters China. Trained at <strong>Miskatonic University</strong> to investigate the unexplained, they soon discover that beneath the surface of a peaceful empire lies chaos, madness, and ancient secrets.</span>
                            <span class="lang-zh">1798年，每位主角进入中国。作为在<strong>密斯卡塔尼克大学</strong>受训调查未解之谜的毕业生，他们很快发现，在和平帝国的表象之下，潜藏着混乱、疯狂与古老的秘密。</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-red-900/50 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                         <div class="text-center">
                            <p class="text-red-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase mb-2">Primary Influence</p>
                            <p class="text-white font-serif text-lg">Chinese Folklore</p>
                         </div>
                         <div class="text-center">
                            <p class="text-red-500 text-xs font-mono uppercase mb-2">Secondary Influence</p>
                            <p class="text-white font-serif text-lg">Cthulhu Mythos</p>
                         </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </main>

    <!-- Script -->
    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();

        function toggleMobileMenu() {
            const menu = document.getElementById('mobile-menu');
            if (menu.classList.contains('hidden')) {
                menu.classList.remove('hidden');
            } else {
                menu.classList.add('hidden');
            }
        }

        function toggleLang() {
            const body = document.body;
            if (body.classList.contains('zh-mode')) {
                body.classList.remove('zh-mode');
            } else {
                body.classList.add('zh-mode');
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>